<plot>Fellow shopgirls and roommates Jerry, Connie and Franky take different paths in the big city. Connie has an affair with David, son of the department store owner, and when he dumps her she kills herself. Franky marries Marty without knowing he's a crook, but Jerry helps her out of this and Franky back goes to her mother's farm. Jerry has resisted Tony, elder son of the store owner, and sadly believes that virtue will be her only reward, but things finally get better with Tony.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?417438</url></doc>
